body.p: The following Norsemen bought or sold real estate in Chicago during the past week:
G. Haehring to Fish and Roy Hansen: 793 Campbell Avenue. Price, $1.
Frank Zeman to Nels B. Wold: Chicago Avenue, west of Keith Street. Price, $1.
Ole Johnson to Harriett S. Keeney: North 41st Avenue, south of North Avenue. Price, $3,700.
Ingjeld Dahl to Anna Wilson: Francisco Avenue, south of Cortland Street. Price, $2,575.
G. P. Hoffman to Nels B. Wald: Ohio Street, east of Morgan Street. Price, $1.
Ole Anda to Asbjorg C. Anda: Avondale Avenue, north of Crescent Avenue. Price, $700.
F. W. Thies to Robert H. Johnson: Clenlake Avenue, east of Clark Street. Price, $1.
Robert H. Johnson to F. W. Thies: Greenwood Terrace, west of Seminary Avenue. Price, $7,000.
Harriett C. Keeney to Ellen Johnson: North 41st Court, south of Bloomingdale Avenue. Price, $1.
